{"tid":192710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"OL深情寬衣　裸照竟遭洋腸當戰利品「分享」","createTime":"2017-04-08T17:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T14:09:15.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5eda345d9361d341c1d016f755150766cfb7f877","tid":192710,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T17:59:37.000Z","msg":"據了解，被害OL年約20多歲，外型清秀端莊，她的洋男友與她年齡相仿，旅居台灣從事教學工作。去年某天被害女子前往洋男友家中，在濃情密意下將衣物脫到上空，不料洋男這時卻拿出手機，趁女子不及防備拍下半裸照，還立馬傳給朋友「分享」。女子當場阻止洋男友，不料對方還是嘻皮笑臉地傳出照片，讓她感到非常不受尊重，彷彿自己只是某種「戰利品」，因此前往台北地檢署提告，洋男被傳喚到案後也坦承犯行，昨被依妨害秘密罪起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/hot/20170408/1092907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fhot%2F20170408%2F1092907&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=664e2a9a\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/hot/20170408/1092907</a><br />\n<br />\n港女就大方得多"},{"pid":"d4852580753a028d6e327e40afbfb9845ce65c17","tid":192710,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港女就大方得多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i57.tinypic.com/okr593.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi57.tinypic.com%2Fokr593.png&h=b3f4e925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20150430/large/1430395563_5659.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20150430%2Flarge%2F1430395563_5659.png&h=9c9202de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4006b9cb78b61c152bed460ca219a28b6c3a5774","tid":192710,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T20:16:37.000Z","msg":"&gt;旅居台灣從事教學工作<br />\n<br />\n應該係無証工作"},{"pid":"15131d4b76c0fff7a94395bb3cf9a11f9d582334","tid":192710,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T01:34:31.000Z","